# Deterministic line endings for the text formats we diff and hand-edit
# (the vocab CSVs especially: a stray CRLF write causes whole-file phantom
# diffs in the single most-edited data file). Audio is declared binary rather
# than relying on git's content heuristics.
*.csv text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.mp3 binary
